===Noun===
'''squeegee'''

#A tool consisting of a rubber blade at right angles to a handle, used when cleaning glass, especially the [[windscreen]] of a [[vehicle]], to remove soapy water.
#{{slang}} A [[person]] who cleans the [[windscreen]] of a vehicle stopped in [[traffic]] then [[demand]]s [[payment]] from the [[driver]].

